platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: 自然给予人类的甘露是睡眠。这款 App 是你的智能睡眠管家，跟踪并分析睡眠情况，创建个性化睡眠计划，帮你了解情绪和饮食产生的影响，为你提供最合适的建议。

Pillow is stuffed with ways to improve your sleep. The app tracks your z’s, records your moods, and follows your daily routine to help you establish a consistent sleep pattern, night after night. We love the app’s intersection of sleep and data. Tell Pillow about your daily routine—including your mood, meal times, and amount of caffeine you’ve consumed—and it’ll begin to learn what’s helping and hindering you at night.
這個 App 能追蹤你的睡眠狀況，記錄你的心情、膳食和咖啡因攝取量，並關注你的日常生活，以多樣方式助你日漸改善睡眠質素。
這款睡眠追蹤 App 能幫助你記錄睡眠狀況、心情、飲食（包括咖啡因攝取），追蹤日常作息，並提供多種功能來改善你的睡眠品質。
Track your sleep, record your moods and meals (and caffeine intake) and follow your daily routine with the app that’s stuffed with ways to improve your slumber, night after night.
